<!DOCTYPE html>
<html lang="en">
<head>
  <meta charset="UTF-8">
  <meta name="viewport" content="width=device-width, initial-scale=1.0">
  <title>üîê Admin Password Reset - MEDH Foundation</title>
  <style>
    body {
      font-family: 'Segoe UI', Tahoma, Geneva, Verdana, sans-serif;
      line-height: 1.6;
      color: #333;
      margin: 0;
      padding: 0;
      background: linear-gradient(135deg, #667eea 0%, #764ba2 100%);
    }
    .email-wrapper {
      background: linear-gradient(135deg, #667eea 0%, #764ba2 100%);
      padding: 40px 20px;
      min-height: 100vh;
    }
    .container {
      max-width: 650px;
      margin: 0 auto;
      background-color: #ffffff;
      border-radius: 16px;
      box-shadow: 0 20px 40px rgba(0, 0, 0, 0.15);
      overflow: hidden;
    }
    .header {
      background: linear-gradient(135deg, #ff6b35 0%, #f7931e 100%);
      color: white;
      padding: 40px 30px;
      text-align: center;
      position: relative;
    }
    .header::before {
      content: '';
      position: absolute;
      top: 0;
      left: 0;
      right: 0;
      bottom: 0;
      background: url('data:image/svg+xml,<svg xmlns="http://www.w3.org/2000/svg" viewBox="0 0 100 20"><defs><radialGradient id="a" cx=".66" cy=".30" r=".7"><stop offset="0" stop-color="%23ffffff" stop-opacity=".2"/><stop offset=".5" stop-color="%23ffffff" stop-opacity=".05"/><stop offset="1" stop-color="%23ffffff" stop-opacity="0"/></radialGradient></defs><rect width="100" height="20" fill="url(%23a)"/></svg>');
      opacity: 0.3;
    }
    .header-content {
      position: relative;
      z-index: 1;
    }
    .logo {
      font-size: 28px;
      font-weight: 700;
      margin-bottom: 10px;
      letter-spacing: -0.5px;
    }
    .header-subtitle {
      font-size: 16px;
      opacity: 0.9;
      font-weight: 300;
    }
    .admin-badge {
      display: inline-block;
      background: rgba(255, 255, 255, 0.2);
      padding: 8px 16px;
      border-radius: 20px;
      font-size: 14px;
      font-weight: 600;
      margin-top: 15px;
      border: 1px solid rgba(255, 255, 255, 0.3);
    }
    .security-icon {
      display: inline-block;
      width: 80px;
      height: 80px;
      background: rgba(255, 255, 255, 0.2);
      border-radius: 50%;
      margin: 20px 0;
      line-height: 80px;
      font-size: 36px;
    }
    .content {
      padding: 40px 30px;
    }
    .alert-section {
      background: linear-gradient(135deg, #fff3e0, #ffe0b2);
      border: 2px solid #ff9800;
      color: #e65100;
      padding: 25px;
      border-radius: 12px;
      margin: 25px 0;
      text-align: center;
      position: relative;
      overflow: hidden;
    }
    .alert-content {
      position: relative;
      z-index: 1;
    }
    .alert-title {
      font-size: 22px;
      font-weight: 700;
      margin-bottom: 10px;
      display: flex;
      align-items: center;
      justify-content: center;
      gap: 10px;
    }
    .alert-message {
      font-size: 16px;
      line-height: 1.5;
      opacity: 0.95;
    }
    .greeting {
      font-size: 20px;
      font-weight: 600;
      color: #2d3748;
      margin-bottom: 20px;
    }
    .main-message {
      font-size: 16px;
      line-height: 1.7;
      color: #4a5568;
      margin-bottom: 30px;
    }
    .admin-info {
      background: linear-gradient(135deg, #e6fffa 0%, #b2f5ea 100%);
      border-left: 4px solid #38b2ac;
      padding: 20px;
      margin: 25px 0;
      border-radius: 8px;
    }
    .admin-info h3 {
      margin: 0 0 10px 0;
      color: #2c7a7b;
      font-size: 16px;
      display: flex;
      align-items: center;
      gap: 8px;
    }
    .admin-details {
      font-size: 14px;
      color: #2d3748;
    }
    .admin-details div {
      margin: 5px 0;
    }
    .password-section {
      background: linear-gradient(135deg, #f7fafc, #edf2f7);
      border: 2px solid #4299e1;
      border-radius: 12px;
      padding: 30px;
      margin: 30px 0;
      text-align: center;
    }
    .password-label {
      font-size: 14px;
      color: #4a5568;
      margin-bottom: 10px;
      font-weight: 600;
      text-transform: uppercase;
      letter-spacing: 1px;
    }
    .temp-password {
      font-family: 'Courier New', monospace;
      font-size: 24px;
      font-weight: bold;
      color: #2b6cb0;
      letter-spacing: 3px;
      margin: 15px 0;
      padding: 20px;
      background: white;
      border-radius: 8px;
      border: 2px solid #4299e1;
      word-break: break-all;
    }
    .expiry-notice {
      background: linear-gradient(135deg, #fed7d7, #feb2b2);
      border-left: 4px solid #e53e3e;
      padding: 20px;
      margin: 25px 0;
      border-radius: 8px;
      font-size: 14px;
    }
    .expiry-notice strong {
      color: #c53030;
    }
    .security-section {
      background: linear-gradient(135deg, #fff3e0, #ffe0b2);
      border: 2px solid #ff9800;
      border-radius: 12px;
      padding: 25px;
      margin: 25px 0;
    }
    .security-title {
      display: flex;
      align-items: center;
      gap: 10px;
      font-size: 18px;
      font-weight: 700;
      color: #e65100;
      margin-bottom: 15px;
    }
    .security-tips {
      list-style: none;
      padding: 0;
      margin: 0;
    }
    .security-tips li {
      display: flex;
      align-items: flex-start;
      gap: 10px;
      margin-bottom: 12px;
      color: #e65100;
      font-size: 14px;
      line-height: 1.5;
      font-weight: 500;
    }
    .security-tips li::before {
      content: 'üîê';
      font-size: 16px;
      margin-top: 2px;
      flex-shrink: 0;
    }
    .action-buttons {
      display: flex;
      gap: 15px;
      margin: 30px 0;
      flex-wrap: wrap;
    }
    .btn {
      display: inline-flex;
      align-items: center;
      gap: 8px;
      padding: 14px 28px;
      text-decoration: none;
      border-radius: 8px;
      font-weight: 600;
      font-size: 15px;
      transition: all 0.3s ease;
      text-align: center;
      flex: 1;
      justify-content: center;
      min-width: 160px;
    }
    .btn-primary {
      background: linear-gradient(135deg, #4299e1, #3182ce);
      color: white;
      box-shadow: 0 4px 12px rgba(66, 153, 225, 0.3);
    }
    .btn-secondary {
      background: white;
      color: #4299e1;
      border: 2px solid #4299e1;
    }
    .btn:hover {
      transform: translateY(-2px);
      box-shadow: 0 8px 20px rgba(66, 153, 225, 0.4);
    }
    .footer {
      background: #f8fafc;
      padding: 30px;
      text-align: center;
      border-top: 1px solid #e2e8f0;
    }
    .footer-content {
      font-size: 13px;
      color: #718096;
      line-height: 1.6;
    }
    .footer-links {
      margin: 15px 0;
    }
    .footer-links a {
      color: #4299e1;
      text-decoration: none;
      margin: 0 10px;
      font-weight: 500;
    }
    
    @media (max-width: 600px) {
      .email-wrapper {
        padding: 20px 10px;
      }
      .container {
        border-radius: 8px;
      }
      .header, .content {
        padding: 30px 20px;
      }
      .action-buttons {
        flex-direction: column;
      }
      .btn {
        min-width: auto;
      }
    }
  </style>
</head>
<body>
  <div class="email-wrapper">
    <div class="container">
      <div class="header">
        <div class="header-content">
          <div class="logo">üîê MEDH Foundation</div>
          <div class="header-subtitle">Admin Password Reset</div>
          <div class="admin-badge">üëë ADMIN SECURITY</div>
          <div class="security-icon">üîë</div>
        </div>
      </div>
      
      <div class="content">
        <div class="alert-section">
          <div class="alert-content">
            <div class="alert-title">
              <span>üîë</span>
              Admin Password Reset Request
            </div>
            <div class="alert-message">
              A temporary password has been generated for your admin account security.
            </div>
          </div>
        </div>

        <div class="greeting">Hello {{name}},</div>
        
        <div class="main-message">
          We received a request to reset the password for your <strong>MEDH Foundation Admin Account</strong>. For security purposes, we've generated a temporary password that you can use to access your admin portal.
        </div>

        {{#if admin_info}}
        <div class="admin-info">
          <h3>üëë Admin Account Information</h3>
          <div class="admin-details">
            <div><strong>Admin Name:</strong> {{admin_info.name}}</div>
            <div><strong>Email:</strong> {{admin_info.email}}</div>
            {{#if admin_info.department}}<div><strong>Department:</strong> {{admin_info.department}}</div>{{/if}}
            {{#if admin_info.designation}}<div><strong>Designation:</strong> {{admin_info.designation}}</div>{{/if}}
            {{#if admin_info.admin_role}}<div><strong>Admin Role:</strong> {{admin_info.admin_role}}</div>{{/if}}
          </div>
        </div>
        {{/if}}

        <div class="password-section">
          <div class="password-label">Temporary Admin Password</div>
          <div class="temp-password">{{tempPassword}}</div>
          <div style="font-size: 12px; color: #718096; margin-top: 10px;">
            Use this password to login to the admin portal
          </div>
        </div>

        <div class="expiry-notice">
          <strong>‚è∞ URGENT:</strong> This temporary password will expire in <strong>{{expiryTime}}</strong>. You must login and change your password immediately for security.
        </div>

        <div class="action-buttons">
          <a href="{{loginUrl}}" class="btn btn-primary">
            <span>üîê</span>
            Login to Admin Portal
          </a>
          <a href="{{securityUrl}}" class="btn btn-secondary">
            <span>üõ°Ô∏è</span>
            Security Guidelines
          </a>
        </div>

        <div class="security-section">
          <div class="security-title">
            <span>üõ°Ô∏è</span>
            Critical Admin Security Requirements
          </div>
          <ul class="security-tips">
            <li>Login immediately and change your password</li>
            <li>Use a strong password with at least 12 characters</li>
            <li>Include uppercase, lowercase, numbers, and special characters</li>
            <li>Never reuse passwords from other accounts</li>
            <li>Enable two-factor authentication if available</li>
            <li>Always logout from admin sessions when done</li>
            <li>Report any suspicious activity immediately</li>
          </ul>
        </div>

        <p style="margin-top: 30px; padding: 20px; background: #fed7d7; border-radius: 8px; border-left: 4px solid #e53e3e; color: #742a2a;">
          <strong>üö® SECURITY ALERT:</strong> If you did not request this password reset, contact our security team immediately at <strong>security@medh.co</strong>. Your admin account may be compromised.
        </p>

        <div style="margin-top: 30px; text-align: center; color: #718096;">
          <p><strong>This is a secure admin password reset notification.</strong></p>
          <p style="font-weight: 600;">Emergency Contact: <a href="mailto:security@medh.co" style="color: #4299e1;">security@medh.co</a> | Hotline: +91-XXX-XXX-XXXX</p>
        </div>
        
        <p style="margin-top: 30px;">
          Best regards,<br>
          <strong>The MEDH Foundation Security Team</strong><br>
          <em>Admin Portal Security Division</em>
        </p>
      </div>
      
      <div class="footer">
        <div class="footer-content">
          <div style="font-weight: 600; margin-bottom: 10px;">MEDH Foundation - Admin Security</div>
          <div>Protecting educational excellence through secure administration</div>
          
          <div class="footer-links">
            <a href="{{helpUrl}}">Admin Help</a>
            <a href="{{securityUrl}}">Security Guide</a>
            <a href="{{privacyUrl}}">Privacy Policy</a>
            <a href="{{contactUrl}}">Emergency Support</a>
          </div>
          
          <div>¬© {{currentYear}} MEDH Foundation. All rights reserved.</div>
          <div style="margin-top: 10px;">This admin security email was sent to <strong>{{email}}</strong></div>
          
          <div style="font-size: 11px; color: #a0aec0; margin-top: 15px;">
            Admin security notifications are mandatory and cannot be disabled.<br>
            This email contains sensitive information - handle with appropriate security measures.
          </div>
        </div>
      </div>
    </div>
  </div>
</body>
</html>
